# Installation instructions:
# 1. Install system dependencies first:
#    - Windows: Download and install Microsoft Visual C++ Build Tools
#    - Linux: sudo apt-get install portaudio19-dev python3-pyaudio
#    - macOS: brew install portaudio
#
# 2. Install Python packages:
#    pip install -r voice_requirements.txt
#
# 3. For Azure TTS, set environment variables:
#    - AZURE_SPEECH_KEY
#    - AZURE_SPEECH_REGION
#
# 4. For Google Cloud TTS, set up service account and:
#    - GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS
#
# 5. For OpenAI TTS, set:
#    - OPENAI_API_KEY
